Individual




Portia Sue Perrotty



Ms. Portia S. Perrotty is Independent Non-Executive Chairman at Global Net Lease, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer at AFM Financial Services LLC, Chairman at KnowledgeFlow, Inc. and Chairman-Development Board at Girl Scouts of Eastern Pennsylvania. She is on the Board of Directors at Axar Acquisition Corp., New York REIT, Inc., American Realty Capital Healthcare Trust III, Inc., ARC Acquisition Corp., Albright College and Berks County Community Foundation, Inc. Ms. Perrotty was previously employed as an Independent Director by American Realty Capital Healthcare Trust, Inc., an Independent Director by American Realty Capital Hospitality Trust, Inc., an Independent Director by American Realty Capital Daily Net Asset Value Trust, Inc., and Executive Vice President by First Union Corp. She received her undergraduate degree from Albright College.



