Insider Activity


Individual




Portia Sue Perrotty



Ms. Portia S. Perrotty is Independent Non-Executive Chairman at Global Net Lease, Inc., Independent Director at AR Capital Acquisition Corp., Independent Director at New York REIT, Inc., Independent Director at American Realty Capital Healthcare Trust III, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer at AFM Financial Services LLC, Chairman at KnowledgeFlow, Inc., Chairman-Development Board at Girl Scouts of Eastern Pennsylvania and Independent Director at ARC Acquisition Corp. She is on the Board of Directors at AR Capital Acquisition Corp., New York REIT, Inc., American Realty Capital Healthcare Trust III, Inc., ARC Acquisition Corp., Albright College and Berks County Community Foundation, Inc. 
Ms. Perrotty was previously employed as Independent Director by American Realty Capital Healthcare Trust, Inc., Independent Director by American Realty Capital Hospitality Trust, Inc., and Independent Director by American Realty Capital Daily Net Asset Value Trust, Inc. 
She received her undergraduate degree from Albright College.



